" Fugitive mapping
nmap <Space>gs :Gstatus<cr>
nmap <Space>gd :Gdiff<cr>
nmap <Space>ga :Gwrite<cr>
nmap <Space>gr :Gread<cr>
nmap <Space>gc :Gcommit<cr>
nmap <Space>gb :Git blame<cr>
nmap <Space>go :Gbrowse<cr>
xnoremap <Space>go :Gbrowse<cr>
nmap <Space>gre :silent! Ggrep<Space>

nmap <Space>gp :Git p<cr>

" grep検索の実行後にQuickFix Listを表示する
autocmd QuickFixCmdPost *grep* cwindow
